  Upresing for Higher Details

In this video, I'm going to show you how I go about upresing images and videos using a few of my favorite tools. Let's not gloss over the elephant in the room here, Topaz Video AI and Gigapixel AI are both fairly expensive tools. However, I believe that if we are going to tell convincing stories we need to shoot for the best quality possible. A simple corner cut in quality can make the difference between a captivating shot and a boring one.

I will also provide you with the files to follow along below. You will also have examples of the before and after images to compare and contrast at AI's performance.

Link to Resources:

  • BigJPG
  • Gigapixel AI
  • Topaz Video AI
